func (s *String) ReadASN1Enum(out *int) bool {
	var bytes String
	var i int64
	if !s.ReadASN1(&bytes, asn1.ENUM) || !checkASN1Integer(bytes) || !asn1Signed(&i, bytes) {
		return false
	}
	if int64(int(i)) != i {
		return false
	}
	*out = int(i)
	return true
}
